tellung und Rezeption geprüft. Ergebnis dieser Studie ist eine konzise Quellenkritik digitaler Zeugnisse, ihr Dispositiv.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jan 2019) 4aDigital History. 4aDigital history. 4aErinnerung. 4aGeschichtstheorie. 4aHolocaust. 4aremembrance. 4atheory of history.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105558750 cprintz978311055577640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110558036423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110558036.jpg  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017